title: The Cannibal Cafe? Murder or Volunteer?
description:
Hi Friends!
Hope your day is off to a good start. Today I wanted to talk about Armin Meiwes and what the hell was going on over there, I mean he was trying to cook sausage and eat it, I mean, yep he did that. 
Did he REALLY deserve the sentencing he got if someone WILLINGLY participated? Weird case right? Least he’s vegan now, that’s good. 
Hope you have a wonderful day today, make good choices and let me know who you want me to talk about next week!
Love and appreciate you guys so much!! Please be safe out there. 
x o
Bailey Sarian
